Your private car service receives terminal assignment notifications through airport operations, not airline systems. This means they're working with a different information source than your flight tracking app. When weather delays hit, airline apps update passenger information immediately, but ground transportation companies receive terminal updates on a separate timeline that can lag 15-30 minutes behind.

